&lt;p&gt;This is a rare seat at the table. As Chief of Staff to the Chief Business Officer, you’ll be the strategic partner and proxy at the center of a high-growth, multi-product company, shaping commercial strategy, driving cross-functional alignment, and turning the CBO’s priorities into results. We’re scaling past 1,000 employees at 60%+ YoY growth, and this is the role that makes sure we do it with rigor.&lt;/p&gt;
