&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the Cross-Functional Bridge:&lt;/strong&gt; Navigate new and growing teams to pinpoint where finance, legal, or product support is needed to accelerate deal velocity and operational efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the Flywheel of Accountability:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the hub between the CBO and his leadership team, keeping strategic decisions cascading cleanly through the organization, closing communication gaps, and holding teams to their commitments as we scale. Drive weekly leadership meetings, monthly business reviews and quarterly OKRs across the CBO&#39;s organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prep the CBO for High-Stakes Moments&lt;/strong&gt;: Build sharp, data-backed materials for Board meetings, investor updates, and partner reviews, and run deep-dives into our commercial architecture to deliver recommendations that shape strategy. Have a front row seat to the strategy and execution of future fundraising milestones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extend the CBO’s Reach: &lt;/strong&gt;Act as a trusted proxy in rooms where the CBO is at capacity, advance priorities independently, and own the research and prep that powers ELT meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
